{"tha-ap131:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap131:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap131:0.3":"9 Ganthipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap131:1.1":"“Suvannavanno sambuddho, ","tha-ap131:1.2":"vipassi dakkhinaraho; ","tha-ap131:1.3":"Purakkhato savakehi, ","tha-ap131:1.4":"arama abhinikkhami. ","tha-ap131:2.1":"Disvanaham buddhasettham, ","tha-ap131:2.2":"sabbannum tamanasakam; ","tha-ap131:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap131:2.4":"ganthipuppham apujayim. ","tha-ap131:3.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap131:3.2":"dvipadindassa tadino; ","tha-ap131:3.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap131:3.4":"puna vandim tathagatam. ","tha-ap131:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap131:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap131:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap131:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap131:5.1":"Ekatalisito kappe, ","tha-ap131:5.2":"carano nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap131:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap131:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap131:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap131:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap131:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap131:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ganthipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap131:8.1":"Ganthipupphiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}